title: Districto do Funchal (O)
body:
It began to be published on January 16, 1864, and ended on August 5, 1865, with a total of 66 issues.

Another newspaper with the same title was published from May 24, 1877, to April 24, 1878, with a total of 23 issues.

1864: Start of the publication of the newspaper 'Districto do Funchal (O)'
1865: End of the publication of the newspaper 'Districto do Funchal (O)'
1877: Start of the publication of another newspaper with the same title 'Districto do Funchal (O)'
1878: End of the publication of the second newspaper 'Districto do Funchal (O)'
